    "short_description": "Hardy transporters",
    "description": "<p>Carry bonds across rivers and dreams across mountains. Couriers are travelers, conductors, and transporters&mdash;the kind of people who love to travel long distances and meet all kinds of people. Play Couriers if you want to deal with the blessings and misfortunes of nature, to see the length and breadth of the world, and to connect people across all that impossible vastness.</p>",
